   		 cases of ordered and bimodal disordered couplings, respectively. Top figures: single site reconstruction, i.e., one row of the matrix $J$. Bottom figures: couplings are plotted sorted in descending order.}  
   	\label{Jor1_dec}
   \end{figure}

